        Just the other day, I was riding home from my school when I heard about a good friend of mine.  He had been involved in a bicycle accident where he lost control of the bike while going down a hill and hit a car.  He is now in a coma, but it seems that he has a very good chance of recovery(maybe even a full recovery).  I will be spending most of my time now at the hospital, and hopefully, on these forums, for I know that I will not have the time to load these new downloads or even think about playing.  I will be out this weekend too, because of a trip to visit relatives.  I hope you all understand.  May everybody have my best wishes while I am gone.                                                                                                                                                                   William    Player of Wachu and Debben  <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#767676><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub70.ezboard.com/ulorellai.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Lorellai</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 110<br> <font color=#B30000>(12/6/01 5:39:44 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub70.ezboard.com/fdraconisrampantfrm11.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=80.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Real Life Troubles</span><hr size=1> I am so sorry to hear about your friend.  I will keep you both in my thoughts. For a thirteen year old, sir, you certainly have a mature attitude.  I wish you the best, and I will anticipate your return.<br>
<br>
Lorellai/Pipette <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#a8a8a8><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub70.ezboard.com/ukurgnthex.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Kurgn Thex</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 141<br> <font color=#B30000>(12/7/01 7:59:24 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub70.ezboard.com/fdraconisrampantfrm11.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=80.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://www.draconisrampant.org/images/Characters/kurgn.gif WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Real Life Troubles</span><hr size=1> I am sure that Lorellai speaks for us all. <br>
